flares 0.4


This is a SDL demo with graphics reacting to the music, alpha blending and scopes.


Usage:

The following command line parameters are supported:

 -h : help
 -v : version
 -fullscreen : run in fullscreen video mode if possible
 -music <file> : use specified music file (MOD, XM, IT, S3M) instead of
                 the included one


Author: Stephan Uhlmann 


Amiga 68k port by Piotr Bandurski
